#~ msgctxt "UI"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "<h2>Two Factor Authentication</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>First of all, every important change made to user account requires email verification. We furthermore recommend enabling two-factor authentication using either TOTP mobile app or a hardware token (U2F). For even better protection, there is a possibility to lock your payout address so it can be only changed in future by a signed message from said address.</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>How We Store the Coins</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>The pool runs payouts very frequently in order to store as few coins as possible as possible. Out of the few coins that we have to take care of, a certain amount of funds is stored in cold storage – a highly secured offline computer that can only be accessed by a very limited number of people. For this reason, cold storage is very resilient to different kinds of hacking attacks.</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>Access Profiles</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>Our pool also features Access Profiles, which enables you to share access to your account with individuals who are not completely trusted. They are able to view your account and mining information while unable to change important settings such as a payout address. This feature is highly useful for large mining operations and their personnel.</p>\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "<h2>两步验证</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>首先，每项用户账户的变更都需要邮件验证。进一步的说，我们推荐您开启两步验证，不管是用TOTP的手机APP方式也好，还是硬件令牌(U2F)也好。为了更好的保护，您甚至可以锁定您的提现地址，这样的话除非系统收到来自特定地址的签名消息，它就不能被改变。</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>我们如何保存币</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>矿池采用非常频繁的支付用户的收益的方式，保存尽可能少量的币。除了这些我们关注的非常少量的币，一些数量的币也被储存在冷储存里 - 一台高度安全的，只能被极少数人接触的离线计算机。而这一来，我们的冷储存就能够抵御各种形式的黑客攻击。</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>访问配置</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>我们的矿池也提供访问配置这一功能，它能让您能够将您的账户设置不同的访问权限，用于分享给您不完全信任的人使用。这一功能对大型矿场和矿场员工非常有帮助。</p>\n"

#~ msgctxt "Intro"
#~ msgid "Worker States (Changes)"
#~ msgstr "矿工状态（变更）"

#~ msgctxt "UI"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "<p>For the majority of pools, miners have few to none options how to verify if data (especially the pool hash rate) presented by the pool operator are correct. Since we are big fans of cryptography and the Don't Trust, Verify approach, we have developed and implemented a unique feature called Hash Rate Proof.</p>\n"
#~ "<p>We collect and publish accurate data with certain unique characteristics from our miners. Such data cannot be counterfeited because a certain amount of work has to be done in the order they are generated. You can imagine them as a data (hashes) which did not meet the criteria to be validated as a regular block but were close with their characteristics to it.</p>\n"
#~ "<p>Because we publish all shares with certain difficulty and above, everyone can independently verify how much hash rate we really have and is spent on productive mining! It is the same calculation the pool does for estimating each miner's hash rate - only extended to the pool scale.</p>\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "<p>对于大多数矿池来说，矿工几乎没有或者完全没有办法，验证矿池提供的数据（尤其是矿池算力）是否正确。出于我们对加密技术一直秉承的热爱，且我们不相信验证的方法，所以我们开发了一个叫算力证明的特别功能。</p>\n"
#~ "<p>我们从我们的矿工收集和公布独特准确且不能被伪造的数据。因为这些数据是基于一些具体数量，且必须按一定生成的顺序完成的工作。您能够想象如果这些数据（哈希）没有达到能够被验证为常规区块的要求，但是它们是很接近能够达到被验证为常规区块的特性的。</p>\n"
#~ "<p>因为我们公布所有的各种难度的份额（Share），每个人基于此都能够独立地验证他们到底有多少的哈希值，有多少算力在有出块的挖矿中被使用了！这和矿池估算每个矿工的哈希值的算法一样 —— 它只是推广到了整个矿池的规模。</p>\n"

