#~ msgctxt "UI"
#~ msgid ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "<h2>The First Mining Pool</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>In 2010, we were the very first in the world to successfully implement the concept of pooled mining. While many other pools emerged and have ceased to exist, we have been operating continuously and and have mined over 1 million bitcoins to day. The former one-man project was transformed into a professional global operation in 2013.</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>Stratum Protocol</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>In 2012, we introduced the Stratum mining protocol to replace the aging and inefficient getwork protocol. Stratum has been subsequently adopted by not only Bitcoin mining pools but by most cryptocurrency pools in general. We have also further improved the protocol to support newly developed technologies such as the version-rolling AsicBoost.</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>Fixing Mining with Braiins OS</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>In 2018, we launched <a href=\"$bos\" target=\"_blank\">Braiins OS</a>, the first fully open-source cryptocurrency embedded system. The goals are to fix the common mining issues, enable performance tweaks and allow users to take full control of their mining hardware. Braiins OS is completely free to use (and modify) for everyone, however, Slush Pool users will benefit the most from the seamless integration.</p>\n"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "\n"
#~ "<h2>世界上首家矿池</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>在2010年，我们在世界上首次成功应用矿池挖矿的概念。这么多年过去了，许多其他矿池要不就是和我们合并，或者就是他们停止了运营，只有我们一直运营到了今天，而且已经有100万枚比特币在我们的矿池被开采出来。曾今一个人做的项目在2013年也变成了专业的全球运营。</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>阶层协议 Stratum Protocol</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>在2012年，我们引入了阶层Stratum挖矿协议以取代旧的低效率的getwork协议。阶层后来发展成为了不只是比特币矿池，而是大部分加密货币矿池的通用协议。我们也更进一步的改进了协议，以支持新开发的技术，例如版本滚动AsicBoost（Version-rolling AsicBoost）。</p>\n"
#~ "<h2>用Braiins OS矿机固件解决挖矿的问题</h2>\n"
#~ "<p>在2018年，我们发布了<a href=\"$bos\" target=\"_blank\">Braiins OS矿机固件</a>，首个完全开源的加密货币嵌入式系统。这样做的目标是解决常见的挖矿问题，并能够调整性能以及让用户能够完全控制他们的矿机。Braiins OS矿机固件是可以供大家完全免费使用（和修改）的，然而，只有在Slush Pool矿池挖矿才能最大享受到无缝的一体化系统的好处。</p>\n"

